OL,3,CMan who built up #25k debt calls for
OL,4,Ctougher gambling restrictions
OL,6,FA recovering gambling addict from
OL,7,FWiltshire, who built up #25,000 of
OL,8,Fdebt in five years, has said that
OL,9,Fgambling adverts "are grooming the
OL,10,Fnext generation."
OL,12,FChris Spindler, from Swindon, said he
OL,13,Fstarted gambling as soon as he turned
OL,14,F18, and within a few days had accounts
OL,15,Fwith "pretty much every gambling
OL,16,Fwebsite you could think of," as he
OL,17,Fwanted to capitalise on the free spins
OL,18,Fand offers.
