OL,3,CMan who built up #25k debt calls for
OL,4,Ctougher gambling restrictions
OL,6,FHe said his gambling "started off very
OL,7,Fresponsible," but it didn't take long
OL,8,Ffor it to spiral out of control.
OL,10,F"Before long, I was gambling on all
OL,11,Fdifferent types of sports and casino
OL,12,Fgames," he explained.
OL,14,F"It just destroyed every part of my
OL,15,Flife."
OL,17,FAccording to Bristol-based charity Ara
OL,18,FRecovery For All, gambling-related
OL,19,Fharm is on the rise, particularly
OL,20,Famong young people.
