OL,6,FNew figures from the charity reveal it
OL,7,Fsupported 25,000 people in the West
OL,8,FCountry in 2023 - almost twice as many
OL,9,Fas in the previous 12 months.
OL,11,FGuy Hawker, Ara Recovery For All's
OL,12,Fgambling service manager, said
OL,13,Fgambling is becoming more and more
OL,14,Faccessible because "these days
OL,15,Feverybody has a casino in their
OL,16,Fpocket."
