OL,3,CMan who built up #25k debt calls for
OL,4,Ctougher gambling restrictions
OL,6,FChris believes that this, combined
OL,7,Fwith the prevalence of gambling
OL,8,Fadverts, has led to more and more
OL,9,Fpeople struggling with a gambling
OL,10,Faddiction.
OL,12,F"The way it is advertised in my eyes
OL,13,Fis sickening," he said.
OL,15,F"A lot of gambling firms now do
OL,16,Fsponsor football clubs so it's sort of
OL,17,Frammed down people's throats, even if
OL,18,Fyou're not looking for it."
