OL,3,CMan who built up #25k debt calls for
OL,4,Ctougher gambling restrictions
OL,6,FHe added he is particularly worried
OL,7,Fabout the impact gambling adverts are
OL,8,Fhaving on children and young people,
OL,9,Fand has started sharing videos on
OL,10,FTikTok.
OL,12,F"It's very glamourised, but 99% of the
OL,13,Ftime, it's not great. It's not all
OL,14,Fthese bright lights and winning
OL,15,Fmoney," he said.
OL,17,F"In my eyes, they're sort of grooming
OL,18,Fthe next generation of gamblers."
