OL,6,FPremier League football clubs have
OL,7,Fagreed to withdraw gambling
OL,8,Fsponsorship from the front of matchday
OL,9,Fshirts.
OL,11,FA Premier League spokesperson said:
OL,12,F"The Premier League is working with
OL,13,Fother sports on the development of a
OL,14,Fnew code for responsible gambling
OL,15,Fsponsorship.
OL,17,F"To assist clubs with their transition
OL,18,Faway from shirt-front gambling
OL,19,Fsponsorship, the collective agreement
OL,20,Fwith begin at the end of the 2025-26
OL,21,Fseason."
